http://i.imgur.com/tCYjWHG.jpg

A strong hand of cards and a mind as sharp as a swordfish's, well, sword are all you need for Sharky's and Clowny's latest romp! And if a single adventure weren't exciting enough, they don't just have to take care of case of maritime sabotage, but also have to shed some light on some blatant egg thievery. Join the two jolly friends on their quest to solve more than 70 exciting maritime comic-style solitaire levels and help them fight a few sinister level bosses while you're at it. Juicy rewards await you in the deep sea casino, and you can use them to buy 10 mighty power-up cards to help Sharky and Clowny in their card battle against the forces of evil.

Features:
- Help Clowny and Sharky find out why the ship suddenly sunk
- Play a huge variety of challenging solitaire levels full of surprise
- Discover power-up cards, achievements and exciting boss battles
- Enjoy hilarious dialogues and lively comic-style stories and backgrounds

System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP or better.
Processor: Pentium 4 or better.
Processor Speed: 1GHz or better.
System RAM: 512 MB or more.
Video RAM: 32 MB or more.
Hard Drive: 130 MB free hard drive space or more.
Resolution: 1024x768 or higher.
